::Shadow Wing::

She got up from her chair and slammed her fist into the wall.  She 
hit the wall a few more times and knelt down on her knees.
she started to sob a bit. "What will it take? I don't want to impress 
him.  All I ever wanted, since I met him, was to make him happy.  And 
all I have done is fail at every attemp."  she just sat there and 
cried.
